'''拉法乌·马伊卡'''（{{lang-pl|Rafał Majka}}，波兰语发音：{{IPAc-pl|'|r|a|f|a|ł|-|'|m|a|j|k|a}}，{{bd|1989年|9月12日||}}）生于小波兰省Zegartowice，是一名波兰男子自行车运动员，主攻公路自行车<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ma/rafal-majka-1.html|title=Rafał Majka|work=Sport Reference|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827142609/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ma/rafal-majka-1.html|archivedate=2019-08-27}}</ref>，擅长爬坡路段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.velonation.com/News/ID/12854/Majka-renews-contract-with-Saxo-Bank-Tinkoff-Bank.aspx|title=Majka renews contract with Saxo Bank-Tinkoff Bank|work=VeloNation|date=2012-09-13|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224334/http://www.velonation.com/News/ID/12854/Majka-renews-contract-with-Saxo-Bank-Tinkoff-Bank.aspx|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>。他在童年时曾接触[[足球|足球]]，12岁时改练习自行车，14岁时他在一场青年比赛中被教练Zbigniew Klęk看中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radiokrakow.pl/www/index.nsf/ID/JNII-97FPLX|script-title=pl:Małopolanie jadą w wyścigu Giro d'Italia|date=2013-05-06|accessdate=2013-05-21|publisher={{lang|pl|Radio Kraków}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521182357/http://www.radiokrakow.pl/www/index.nsf/ID/JNII-97FPLX|archivedate=2013-05-21}}</ref>。2011年，他加入盛宝银行车队，这是他加入的首个职业车队<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dziennikpolski24.pl/vacansoleil-zaangazowal-wychowanka-krakusa/ar/3088882|script-title=pl:Vacansoleil zaangażował wychowanka Krakusa|work={{lang|pl|Dziennik Polski}}|date=2011-11-24|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/x56ym|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>。

